
  Salandit    Poison Type Pokémon

  It burns its bodily fluids to 
  create a poisonous gas.  When 
  its enemies become disoriented 
  from inhaling the gas, it attacks 
  them. 
	Evolution Chain
      Salandit ► Salazzle

